quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  35,1,EL-HEMDU LILLAHI FATIRI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI XHA’ILIL-MELA’IKETI RUSULÆN ‘ULI ‘EXHNIHETIN METHNA WE THULATHE WE RUBA’A JEZIDU FIL-HALKI MA JESHA’U ‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN KADIRUN
  35,2,MA JEFTEHI ELLAHU LILNNASI MIN REHMETIN FELA MUMSIKE LEHA WE MA JUMSIK FELA MURSILE LEHU MIN BA’DIHI WE HUWEL-’AZIZUL-HEKIMU
  35,3,JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NASU EDHKURU NI’METEL-LAHI ‘ALEJKUM HEL MIN HALIKIN GAJRU ELLAHI JERZUKUKUM MINE ES-SEMA’I WEL-’ERDI LA ‘ILAHE ‘ILLA HUWE FE’ENNA TU’UFEKUNE
  35,4,WE ‘IN JUKEDHDHIBUKE FEKAD KUDHDHIBET RUSULUN MIN KABLIKE WE ‘ILA ELLAHI TURXHA’UL-’UMURU
  35,5,JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NASU ‘INNE WA’DEL-LAHI HEKKUN FELA TEGURRENNEKUMUL-HEJA ETU ED-DUNJA WE LA JEGURRENNEKUM BILLAHIL-GARURU
  35,6,‘INNE ESH-SHEJTANE LEKUM ‘ADUWUN FE ETTEHIDHUHU ‘ADUWÆN ‘INNEMA JED’U HIZBEHU LIJEKUNU MIN ‘ESHABI ES-SA’IRI
  35,7,EL-LEDHINE KEFERU LEHUM ‘ADHABUN SHEDIDUN WEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI LEHUM MEGFIRETUN WE ‘EXHRUN KEBIRUN